	(text "CLOCK  -  LSE 32.768 kHz   (Y1  Q13FC13500004, LCSC C32346)\n\n  Y1.1 -> OSC32_IN  (PC14)\n  Y1.2 -> OSC32_OUT (PC15)\n  C24 / C25 -> LSE load caps to GND   (12pF shown)\n\nLoad caps: CL match = 2*(CL - Cstray); trim with the RTC SMOOTHCALIB.\nDrives the RTC for sleep timing."
